   - â¡ï¸ Iterate through the array.
   - ğŸ”„ Adjust current value based on previous flips.
   - âœ… Perform a flip if the current value is `0`.
   - ğŸš« If a flip is needed but not possible, return `-1`.

This solution efficiently tracks and performs flips using a sliding window and map, ensuring the minimum number of flips are performed.
